    <h2>Real Estate Law </h2>
      
    <p> At James Andersen, Attorney at Law, I am ready to assist with your real estate needs.  With over <strong>44 years of legal experience</strong> , I am able to counsel clients on simple to complex real estate transactions.</p>
   
